        "semicol",
        "hashtag"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "日期格式就用YYYY-MM-DD。标题里直接放这些符号，比如写成\"#; Gantt Diagrams Allow Semicolons and Hashtags #;!\"这种形式，我们想验证一下这些符号在标题里的显示效果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "semicol",
        "hashtag"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，标题已设置。我同时加上了可访问性描述：accTitle设为\"A simple sample gantt diagram\"，accDescr描述为\"2 sections with 2 tasks each, from 2014\"。现在开始画第一个section，名称也想带符号，叫\"#;Section\"可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "accTitle",
        "accDescr",
        "section",
        "semicol",
        "hashtag"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以。第一个section里放两个任务：第一个叫\"#;A task\"，从2014-01-01开始持续30天，标记为a1；第二个叫\"#;Another task\"，紧跟在a1后面，持续20天。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section",
        "task",
        "semicol",
        "hashtag",
        "duration",
        "dependency"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "第一个section完成了。第二个section我打算叫\"#;Another\"，里面第一个任务\"Task in sec\"从2014-01-12开始持续12天。第二个任务\"another task\"需要您确认一下开始时间。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section",
        "task",
        "semicol",
        "hashtag",
        "date"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "第二个任务\"another task\"没有指定开始日期，只给了24天的工期。这个应该是从上一个任务结束自动接续，还是有什么其他安排？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "task",
        "duration",
        "dependency"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "按甘特图的语法，如果只写工期不写开始时间，默认是从图表起始日期开始，或者紧接section内前一个任务。这里\"another task\"放在\"Task in sec\"后面，应该理解为接续关系。我按24d直接画，您看这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
